  U7 chit8 hang7 hou7 i put-chi2 eng5-kng, chiu7-si7 iau2-be7 chhut-hoat e5 tai7-seng, i u7 tit-tioh8 I5-to-li7-a Lu2-ong5 e5 chan3-seng5. Lu2-ong5 chhiaN2 Li2-un-su-teng khi3 kau3 ong5-kiong hou7 i saN-kiN3. Koh chin ho2 khoan2-thai7 i. 
  Li2-un-su-teng hou7 cheng3-lang5 ka7 i song3-piat8 liau2-au7, kap Bok8-su-niu5 i2-kip8 i e5 soe3-kiaN2 Ou5-se (Oswell)ti7 3 geh8 10 jit8 (1858 ni5) li7-khui pun2-kok, tah chun5 beh khi3 A-hui-li7-ka. I siong5-siong5 khou2-khng3 i e5 tang5-phoaN7 kong2, Na7-si7 kau3 A-hui-li7-ka, in tai7-ke tioh8 chin7 sou2 oe7--e5 lai5 pang-chan7, lai5 khan-seng5, lai5 khoan2-thai7 hiah e5 bo5 khai-hoa3 e5 ou-bin7 lang5. Tioh8 hou7 in tit-tioh8 to7-tek e5 ka3-si7. Ia7 tioh8 hou7 in e5 seng-oah8 khah an-teng7. 
  Kau3-ui7 e5 si5, in ko2-jian5 u7 an2-ni kiaN5. Tai7-ke put-chi2 thiaN3-sioh hia e5 pun2-toe7 lang5. Sou2-i2 kau3 ti7 kin-a2-jit8, put-lun7 sim2-mih8 chhut-goa7 lang5 na7 khi3 kau3 in hia, ia7 m7-bian2 kiaN u7 sim2-mih8 siong-hai7 Che long2 si7 ui7-tioh8 Li2-un-su-teng e5 gau5 ka3-si7 kap gau5 thiaN3-thang3 hiah e5 lang5. 
  Chun5 kau3 A-hui-li7-ka e5 lam5-peng5, Li2-un-su-teng Bok8-su-niu5 e5 sin-the2 na2 ku2 na2 bo5 iong2-kiaN7, sou2-i2 i kap soe3-kiaN2 Ou5-se tiam3 ti7 hia liau5-iong2. Li2-un-su-teng pun2-sin kap tang5-phoaN7 choe3-tin7 tit8-tit8 kau3 Sam-pi2-se ho5 khau2. Siang7 hit si5 i soa3 toa3 chit8 chiah soe3-chiah he2-chun5 ho7-choe3 Ma7-lo5 (Ma-Robert)kau3 ti7 ho5 khau2. Tui3 chia khi2-sin, in sai2 hit chiah he2-chun5 tit8-tit8 kau3 ho5 e5 lai7-toe7. 
  Ti7 9 geh8 8 jit8 (1858 ni5), chun5 pha-tiaN3 ti7 Te3-te7. Li2-un-su-teng chiuN7-liok8 kap i nng7 ni5 cheng5 sou2 pang3 he7-teh e5 Ma2-ko-lo5 lang5 koh saN-kiN3. In khoaN3-kiN3 i koh-chai3 lai5, hoaN-hi2, tio5-thiau3 kau3 boe7-oe7 kong2--tit. In ti7 soaN-lai7 tit8-tit8 tan2 nng7-ni5 ku2. TaN chu2-lang5 i2-keng koh lai5, in boe7 kim3-tit toa7 hoaN-hi2. Koh-chai3 tit-tioh8 in e5 chu2-lang5 toa3 choe7-choe7 mih8 lai5 sang3 in, in e5 hoaN-hi2 koh-khah kong2 boe7 chin7. 
  In tui3 Sam-pi2-se ho5 khau2 sai2 chit chiah he2-chun5,ti7 lou7-tiong u7 tu2-tioh8 khoe-lau5, sou2-i2 u7 si5 sai2 long2 boe7 chin3. Ui7-tioh8 chit e5 in-toaN, in chiu7 sai2 tui3 pat8 tiau5 khi2-khi3. Chit tiau5 Se-le2 ho5 (Shire River) chin oan-oat, koh long2 si7 thoaN. Sou2-i2 sai2 chun5 tui3 hia khi3 sit8-chai7 put-chi2 khun3-lan5. Keng-ke3 loa7-choe7 kan-khou2, kiaN5 kui2 pah Eng-li2, in chiah kau3 lai7-toe7 khah koan5 e5 sou2-chai7. Ti7 hia khi3-hau7 cham2-jian5 khah ho2. In tai7-ke e5 sin-the2 ia7 khah iong2-kiaN7. 
  Pi2-kau3 pat8 sou2-chai7, chit toe7-hng e5 lang5 ia7 khah bun5-beng5. In oe7-hiau2 phah thih, oe7-hiau2 sio hui5, oe7-hiau2 cheng3 mi5-hoe kap pat8-hang7 chhai3-soe. 
  Ti7 9 geh8 16 jit8 (1859 ni5), Li2-un-su-teng thau5-pai2 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 e5 chiaN2-chui2 e5 toa7 ou5. Tng5 u7 350 Eng-li2. I e5 chui2 ia7 chin chheng. Chit e5 ou5 ho7-choe3 Na5-a2-sah (Nyasa). 
  Kho2-sioh kiaN5 kau3 chit sou2-chai7, i e5 he2-chun5 e7 lau7. Chun5-toe2 long2 si7 khang, khah pou2 ia7 boe7 bat8. Koh in jit8-jit8 sou2 tioh8 eng7 e5 mih8-kiaN7 ia7 chin khiam3. Sou2-i2 Li2-un-su-teng kap i e5 hiaN-ti7 Chha5-li2, kap Ke5 Iok-han7 I-seng chun2-pi7 beh chhoa7 hiah e5 Ma2-ko-lo5 lang5 to3-tng2 khi3 in e5 pun2-hiuN. Na7-si7 in tiong-kan u7 lang5 i2-keng tiam3 ti7 Te3-te7 hiah-nih ku2, koh-chai3 u7 kian3-ti3 ke-koan3, taN soa3 long2 bo5 ai3 to3-tng2 khi3. Chi2-u7 kui2-na7 lang5 hoaN-hi2 kap Li2-un-su-teng choe3-tin7 kiaN5. In sou2 keng-ke3 e5 toe7-hng jin5-sou3 put-chi2 choe7,ia7 chin chhin-chhiat. Na7-si7 ti7 hit sou2-chai7 choe3 kang, kang-chiN5 chin-chiaN3 siok8; chit8 e5 lang5 chit8 jit8 sou2 than3 si7 chio2-chio2. Sou2-i2 hiah e5 Ma2-ko-lo5 lang5 kng mih8 na7-si7 sian7, in chiu7 kau-siap8 chhiaN3 pat8 lang5 lai5 thoe3 in kng. Kang-chiN5 si7 kui2-liap8 siok8-siok8 e5 chu-a2 na7-tiaN7. Tu2-tng7 u7 chit8 e5 pin5-toaN7 koh lau7 e5 Ma2-ko-lo5 lang5 siuN7 sian7 bo5 ai3 kng heng5-li2. I kio3 chit8 e5 siau3-lian5--e5 lai5 thoe3 i, hit e5 lang5 lian5-soa3 ka7 i thoe3 kng saN-jit8 ku2. I sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 kang-chiN5 si7 chit8 nia2 bo5 lang5 ai3, phoa3-phoa3 e5 khou3 na7-tiaN7. 
  Kho2-sioh ti7 chiah e5 sou2-chai7 u7 Pho5-to5-ga5 lang5 tauh8-tauh8 ai3 thau liah8 lang5 khi3 boe7 choe3 lou5-chai5. Koh khi3 bo5 loa7 hng7, in thiaN-kiN3 u7 kui2-na7 e5 Soan-kau3-su tiam3 ti7 Lin5-ian3-ti5 (Linyanti) u7 tu2-tioh8 phoa3-piN7. U7 e5 soa3 si2. Ki5-u5-e5 toa3 boe7 tiau5, kou-put-chiong li7-khui in e5 thoan5-to7 toe7, koh-chai3 to3-tng2 kau3 pun2-kok. In chit kui2 lang5 peng5-sou3 teh choe3 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang ti7 Ma2-ko-lo5 lang5 e5 tiong-kan. 
  Koh-chai3 saN geh8 jit8 ku2, Li2-un-su-teng kap i e5 tang5-phoaN7 tit8-tit8 kiaN5 kau3 Ma2-ko-lo5 lang5 e5 toe7-hng. In e5 thau5-bak8 Se-ke-le2-tu5 khoaN3-kiN3 in lai5, sim-koaN kau3-kek8 hoaN-hi2. I kong2, sui-jian5 i tan2 kui2-na7 ni5 ku2, i chai Li2-un-su-teng u7 chit8 jit8 tek-khak oe7 koh-chai3 lai5. 
  Chhit ni5 cheng5, Li2-un-su-teng sou2 kau-tai7 in kou3 e5 mih8-kiaN7 tak8-hang7 long2 ti7-teh. Long2 tit-tioh8 Se-ke-le2-tu5 kap i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 chiau3-kou3. Bo5 chit8 hang7 sit-loh8. Sit8-chai7 in chin chin7-tiong. Na7 m7-si7 Li2-un-su-teng pun2-sin gau5 thiaN3-thang3 chiah e5 ou-bin7 lang5, in tek-khak boe7 oe7 chin7-tiong kau3 an2-ni. 
  Ti7 chit si5, hit chiah he2-chun5 (Ma7-lo5) na2 ku2 na2 phaiN2-khi3. Tauh8-tauh8 teh siu-li2, na7-si7 bo5 hoat-tou7. Kau3 lou7-be2 kou-put-chiong tioh8 ka7 i pang3-sak. TaN Li2-un-su-teng na7-si7 chhut-goa7 si7 eng7 soe3 chiah chun5-a2. 
  Ti7 1861 ni5, i kap i e5 tang5-phoaN7 eng7 sio2-chun5 tit8-tit8 sai2 kau3 hai2-khau2 e5 sou2-chai7. Kau3-ui7 e5 si5, in tit-tioh8 kui2-na7 e5 kou2 peng5-iu2 e5 ho2 khoan2-thai7. Koh u7 siu-tioh8 i e5 ka-chok8 sou2 kia3-lai5 e5 phoe. Hiah e5 phoe sui-bong2 si7 ni5 poaN3 cheng5 sou2 sia2-e5, iau2-ku2 thak8 liau2 hou7 i e5 sim tit-tioh8 chin toa7 e5 an-ui3. 
  Tu2-tioh8 chhi3-lian7
  Ti7 1861 ni5 e5 ni5-thau5, Li2-un-su-teng u7 koh cho7 chit8 chiah sin e5 he2-chun5. Ka7 i ho7 mia5 choe3 Pai2-o-ni5 (Pioneer). In-ui7 hit chiah ku7 e5, i2-keng phaiN2-phaiN2, bo5 lou7-eng7. 
  Siang5 chit chun7, tui3 pun2-kok u7 siau3-lian5 e5 soan-kau3-su, chi3-goan7 beh khi3 A-hui-li7-ka pang-chan7 i thoan5-po3 Chu2 e5 hok-im. In chiah e5 soan-kau3-su tai7-ke put-chi2 u7 hak8-lek8. Koh long2-si7 iu2-beng5 Tai7-hak8 e5 chut-giap8 seng. 
  Chhoa7 chiah e5 soan-kau3-su choe3-tin7 khi3--e5, chiu7-si7 Ma2-khian Kam-tok (Bishop Moekenyie). I u7 chhoa7 gou7 e5 Eng-kok lang5 kap gou7 e5 ou-bin7 lang5 kap i choe3-tin7 khi3. I ng3-bang7 u7 thang chhe7 tu2-ho2 e5 sou2-chai7 lai5 he7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 toe7-ki. 
  TaN u7 sin e5 he2-chun5, Li2-un-su-teng ng3-bang7 chiong-lai5 oe7-tit thang chiong chit chiah chun5 lai5 un7-poaN mih8-kiaN7 kap chai3-kheh. I long2 bo5 phah-sng3 chit chiah sin chun5 oe7 chiah8 hiah chhim-chui2. Hit-si5 hit tiau5 ho5 iu7-koh ta--khi3. Sou2-i2 sui-bong2 u7 chun5, hoan2-tng2 chin put-pian7. Chong2-si7 kou-put-chiong ia7 tioh8 tit8-tit8 sai2 chiuN7 hit tiau5 ho5. I2-goa7 bo5 sim2-mih8 pat8 khoan2 e5 ho2 hoat-tou7. Tai7-ke phah-sng3 na7-si7 khah ban7 hou7-chui2 kau3 e5 si5, chu7-jian5 ti7 tak8 si3-koe3 chui2 oe7 khah chhiong-chiok, hit tiau5 ho5 ia7 oe7 khah chhim. SiuN7-tioh8 chit khoan2 keng2-gu7,i e5 sim-koaN it-hoat na2 kan-lan5. 
  TaN ti7 chit toe7-hng sui-bong2 thou5 chin pui5, lang5-lang5 eng-kai tioh8 chin ho2 khia7-khi2. Chong2-si7 u7 phaiN2-lang5 siong5-siong5 eng7 kiong5 e5 hong-hoat lam7-sam2 lai5 liah8-lang5 khi3 choe3 lou5-chai5. Chhu3 siong5-siong5 hou7 in pang3 he2-sio. Lau7-lang5 hou7 in thai5-si2, siau3-lian5 e5, hou7 in eng7 thih-lian7 lian7; khah iong2-kiaN7 e5,long2 liah8-khi3 boe7 choe3 lou5-le7. Chiah e5 chan5-jim2 e5 lang5 u7 e5 si7 Pho5-to5-ga5 lang5, u7 e5 si7 A-lat-pek lang5. Tu2-tioh8 chit khoan2 e5 su7, choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7 khng3 teh pha-hng, in-ui7 bo5 lang5 thang cheng3-chok. 
  U7 chit8 jit8, Li2-un-su-teng kap Ma2-khian Kam-tok ti7 lai7-soaN e5 sou2-chai7, hut-jian5 tu2-tioh8 chit8 tin7 ou-bin7 lang5 hou7 lang5 eng7 thih-lian7 lian7, teh-beh khan-khi3 boe7. KhoaN3-kiN3 Li2-un-su-teng kap Kam-tok chit8-e7 kau3, chiah e5 phaiN2-lang5 khui-pou7 chiu7 chau2 kau3 chhiu7-na5 lai7. Li2-un-su-teng khoaN3-kiN3 an2-ni, sim-lai7 kau3-kek8 kho2-lin5 hiah e5 siu7 lang5 liah8-e5. In-ui7 in kui toa7-tin7 hou7 lang5 eng7 soh pak8, eng7 thih-lian7 lian7. In e5 seng-khu koh long2 si7 siong. Tai7-ke go7 kau3 san2-san2. KiaN5 oa2 ka7 in khoaN3, Li2-un-su-teng kap Kam-tok it-hoat kho2-lin5 in chiah e5 ou-bin7 lang5. 
  In koaN2-kin2 koah-tng7 sou2 pak8 e5 soh, koh chiong thih-lian7 ka7 i kong3-tng7, hou7 in tai7-ke tit-tioh8 thau2-pang3. In hiah e5 hap8-kiong7 u7 poeh-chap8-si3 lang5. Thau2-pang3 liau2, in ui7-tioh8 kiaN tui3-tek8 soa3 long2 m7-kaN2 chau2. Kan-ta oe7-hiau2 kiu5 Li2-un-su-teng iong5-un2 in kap i choe3-tin7; ng3-bang7 thang tit-tioh8 i e5 ti3-im3. Ma2-khian Kam-tok chin7-lat8 an-ui3 in, soa3 iok beh chhoa7 in koh to3-tng2. I ia7 siong5-siong5 kong2 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 to7-li2 hou7 in thiaN, soa3 chin7 i sou2-oe7--e5 lai5 chiau3-kou3 in. Tui3 chit si5 i2-au7, Li2-un-su-teng u7 kui2-na7 pai2 e5 ki-hoe7 lai5 chin2-kiu3 pat8 e5 lou5-le7. 
  Au7-lai5 i u7 keng2 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7 oa2 ti7 Chi3-hoa3 ou5(Lake Chilwa) kiN5. I ai3 ti7 hia kian3-siat chit8 e5 kau3-hoe7. Tai7-ke khoaN3 hit e5 ui7-ti3 put-chi2 hah8. Hia e5 khi3-hau7 ia7 si7 ho2. Hit te3 e5 lang5 ia7 chin chhin-chhiat. Koh toe7-hng e5 chhut-san2 ia7 si7 choe7. 
  Hiah e5 soan-kau3-su khoaN3-kiN3 chit khoan2 e5 ki-hoe7,tai7-ke koaN2-kin2 ke3-ek8 ai3 khi2 in e5 siok-sia3. In ia7 jit8-jit8 bian2-kiong2 oh8 hiah e5 lang5 e5 khiuN-khau2. Li2-un-su-teng tui3 i e5 keng-giam7, chiong choe7-choe7 hang7 lai5 bian2-le7 chiah e5 sin lai5 e5 soan-kau3-su; kio3 in tioh8 oe7 hiau2 thun-lun2, gau5 jim2-nai7. Au7-lai5 i kap in saN-si5,in-ui7 i pun2-sin ai3 beh khi3 khoaN3 chit e5 Na5-a2-sah ou5 kap i e5 chiu-ui5. I ai3 chai hit toe7-hng e5 khoan2-sit. Ti7 nng7 ni5 cheng5 chit e5 toa7 ou5, ia7 si7 i thau5-pai2 lai5 hoat-kian3-tioh8. Sou2-i2 ou5 e5 chiu-ui5 siN choe3 siaN2 khoan2, ia7 si7 bo5 lang5 chai. Beh khi3 bo5 lang5 bat kau3 e5 sou2-chai7, sit8-chai7 si7 toa7 tham3-hiam2, ia7 si7 u7 gui5-hiam2. 
  Li2-un-su-teng tai7-seng chun2-pi7 chit8 chiah chun5; kau3-giah8 toa7, thang chai3 i kap i e5 tang5-phoaN7. In hap8-kiong7 u7 ji7-chap8 goa7 lang5. Chiong5-tiong u7 i e5 hiaN-ti7 Chha5-li2, koh u7 Ke5 I-seng kap chit8 e5 Eng-kok chui2-siu2. I2-goa7 u7 ji7-chap8 goa7 e5 ou-bin7 lang5. 
  Tai7-seng keng-ke3 hit tiau5 toa7 ho5 kap choe7-choe7 e5 thoaN, in koh geh8 goa7 jit8 ku2, chiu7 kau3 Na5-a2-sah ou5. Ou5 e5 si3-ui5 long2 si7 koan5-soaN, sou2-i2 na7-si7 thau3 hong, ou5 lai7 liam5-piN chiu7 khi2 eng2. Na2 chhin-chhiuN7 Ka-li7-li7 hai2 e5 khoan2-sit. Ti7 chit e5 ou5-kiN5 jin5-sou3 put-chi2 choe7,chong2-si7 hiah e5 lang5 long2 bo5 khai-hoa3, peng5-sou3 koh chin hiong5-ok. In tauh8-tauh8 ai3 chhiuN2-kiap lang5. U7 si5 chiong lang5 soa3 liah8-khi3 boe7 choe3 lou5-chai5. In ia7 chin bo5 sin3-iong7. 
  Koh u7 choe7-choe7 sia7 ti7 chit e5 ou5 e5 pak-si3. In hiah e5 lang5 koh-khah bo5 to7-tek. ChhiuN2 lang5, liah8 lang5,thai5 lang5, pang3-he2 sio chhu3, chit khoan2 chan5-jim2 e5 su7, in khoaN3 choe3 si7 peng5-siong5. Ti7 chit8 ni5 tiong chi3-chio2 u7 chit8-ban7 kau2-chheng lang5 hou7 in liah8-khi3 boe7 choe3 lou5-chai5. Hou7 in liah8 bo5 khi3, tu2-tioh8 si2-sit e5 siau3-giah8 sng3 boe7 liau2. Peng5-kun-chhe2, ti7 gou7 e5 lang5 e5 tiong-kan, u7 si3 e5 hou7 in thai5-si2, u7 chit8 e5 hou7 in liah8-khi3. Tui3 an2-ni lai5 ka7 i sng3, tu2-tioh8 thai5-si2--e5,mui2 ni5 sng3 si7 kui2-na7 ban7. 
  Li2-un-su-teng kap i e5 tang5-phoaN7, ti7 hit toe7-hng lu2-heng5 nng7, saN geh8 jit8 ku2, chiah koh loh8 lam5-peng5. In ti7 lou7-tiong thiaN-kiN3 hiah e5 soan-kau3-su, tit-tioh8 chin ho2 ki-hoe7 teh choe3 Chu2 e5 kang. Chun5 kun7-oa2 e5 si5, Ma2-khian Kam-tok kap hit kui2 e5 soan-kau3-su,chit8-e7 khoaN3-kiN3 Li2-un-su-teng kap i e5 tang5-phoaN7 ti7 chun5-nih, tai7-ke hoaN-hi2 kau3 boe7-kou3-tit. In khia7 ti7 ho5-kiN chhiu2 na2 iat8, Li2-un-su-teng e5 chun5 te3 ho5-chui2 na2 lau5. Chun5 khi3 kau3 hng7-hng7, hiah e5 soan-kau3-su chiah oat8 to3-tng2-khi3. Che si7 lou7-be2 pai2 Ma2-khian Kam-tok khoaN3-kiN3 Li2-un-su-teng e5 bin7. 
